      "para_id": "Q001998.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Lulal of Du-eden , his master , Urdu-kuga , the shepherd , who provides Nibru with everything , ..., the spouse looked upon favourably by Inana , built his beloved temple ."
